<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>좌석 선택</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <!-- 예매창 전용 CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/booking-seat.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --cc-primary: #7c3aed;
            --cc-primary-dark: #4c1d95;
            --cc-primary-softer: #f1eafe;
            --cc-text: #1f1b2d;
            --cc-subtext: #5f5870;
            --cc-muted: #8a8299;
            --cc-line: #e8e1f2;
            --cc-bg: #f6f4fb;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html,
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 1120px;
            background: var(--cc-bg);
            color: var(--cc-text);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Noto Sans KR", Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        button,
        select,
        input {
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        button {
            border: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .cc-main {
            padding: 14px;
        }

        .cc-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cc-popup-header {
            height: 54px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            padding: 0 18px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--cc-line);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(43, 21, 91, .06);
        }

        .cc-popup-header__title {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 950;
            color: var(--cc-primary-dark);
        }

        .cc-popup-header__meta {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--cc-muted);
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .cc-popup-close {
            height: 34px;
            padding: 0 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #f3effa;
            color: var(--cc-primary-dark);
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .cc-card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--cc-line);
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(43, 21, 91, .06);
        }

        .cc-btn {
            height: 46px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 950;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .cc-btn--full {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .cc-btn--primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #4c1d95);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .cc-btn--outline {
            border: 1px solid var(--cc-line);
            background: #fff;
            color: var(--cc-primary-dark);
        }

        .cc-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 26px;
            padding: 0 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .cc-badge--fill {
            background: var(--cc-primary);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .cc-dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
        }

        .cc-dot--vip { background: #7c3aed; }
        .cc-dot--r { background: #60a5fa; }
        .cc-dot--s { background: #5eead4; }
        .cc-dot--a { background: #fbbf24; }
        .cc-dot--gray { background: #d8d2e2; }

        .cc-select {
            border: 1px solid var(--cc-line);
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #fff;
            color: var(--cc-text);
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<main class="cc-main">
    <div class="cc-container">
        <header class="cc-popup-header">
            <div>
                <div class="cc-popup-header__title">🎫 좌석 선택</div>
                <div class="cc-popup-header__meta">좌석 선택 후 10분 이내에 결제를 진행해주세요.</div>
            </div>
            <button type="button" class="cc-popup-close" onclick="window.close()">창 닫기</button>
        </header>
        <div class="cc-stepper" aria-label="예매 진행 단계">
            <div class="cc-step is-done"><span class="cc-step__num">✓</span>예매정보</div>
            <span class="cc-step-line"></span>
            <div class="cc-step is-active"><span class="cc-step__num">2</span>좌석선택</div>
            <span class="cc-step-line"></span>
            <div class="cc-step"><span class="cc-step__num">3</span>결제</div>
            <span class="cc-step-line"></span>
            <div class="cc-step"><span class="cc-step__num">4</span>완료</div>
        </div>

        <section class="cc-seat-layout">
            <aside>
                <div class="cc-card cc-booking-summary">
                    <div class="cc-booking-summary__dark">
                        <span class="cc-badge cc-badge--fill">단독판매</span>
                        <h2>{{#concert.title}}{{concert.title}}{{/concert.title}}{{^concert.title}}
                            2026 무명전설 전국투어 콘서트 - 서울{{/concert.title}}</h2>
                        <p class="cc-booking-summary__line">
                            📅 {{#sessionText}}{{sessionText}}{{/sessionText}}{{^sessionText}}
                            2026.06.27 (토) 18:00{{/sessionText}}</p>
                        <p class="cc-booking-summary__line">📍 {{#venueText}}{{venueText}}{{/venueText}}{{^venueText}}
                            서울 · 올림픽공원 올림픽홀{{/venueText}}</p>
                        <div class="cc-booking-summary__poster"><img
                                src="{{#concert.posterUrl}}{{concert.posterUrl}}{{/concert.posterUrl}}{{^concert.posterUrl}}/images/sample/poster-legend-seoul.svg{{/concert.posterUrl}}"
                                alt="공연 포스터"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cc-card cc-booking-info">
                    <h3>예매 정보</h3>
                    <div class="cc-mini-row">
                        <b>관람일시</b><span>{{#sessionText}}{{sessionText}}{{/sessionText}}{{^sessionText}}
                        2026.06.27 (토) 18:00{{/sessionText}}</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-mini-row"><b>관람장소</b><span>{{#venueName}}{{venueName}}{{/venueName}}{{^venueName}}
                        올림픽공원 올림픽홀{{/venueName}}</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-mini-row"><b>관람등급</b><span>만 7세 이상</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-mini-row"><b>관람시간</b><span>120분</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-mini-row"><b>매수제한</b><span>회차당 1인 4매</span></div>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <section class="cc-card cc-seat-map-card">
                <div class="cc-seat-map-head">
                    <div class="cc-grade-list">
                        <h3>좌석 등급</h3>
                        {{#grades}}
                            <div class="cc-grade-row"><i class="cc-dot cc-dot--{{gradeClass}}"></i><span>{{name}}
                                <small>{{priceText}}</small></span></div>
                        {{/grades}}
                        {{^grades}}
                            <div class="cc-grade-row"><i class="cc-dot cc-dot--vip"></i><span>VIP<small>154,000원</small></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cc-grade-row"><i
                                    class="cc-dot cc-dot--r"></i><span>R<small>121,000원</small></span></div>
                            <div class="cc-grade-row"><i
                                    class="cc-dot cc-dot--s"></i><span>S<small>99,000원</small></span></div>
                            <div class="cc-grade-row"><i
                                    class="cc-dot cc-dot--a"></i><span>A<small>77,000원</small></span></div>
                        {{/grades}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="cc-stage">STAGE</div>
                    <div class="cc-seat-status">
                        <div><i class="cc-dot cc-dot--vip"></i>선택 좌석</div>
                        <div><i class="cc-dot cc-dot--gray"></i>예매 가능</div>
                        <div><i class="cc-dot cc-dot--a"></i>임시 보관</div>
                        <div><i class="cc-dot cc-dot--gray"></i>매진</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cc-arena" aria-label="좌석 배치도">
                    {{#seatZones}}
                        <section class="cc-zone cc-zone--{{zoneClass}}">
                            <span class="cc-zone__name">{{name}}</span>
                            <div class="cc-zone__dots">
                                {{#seats}}
                                    <button type="button"
                                            class="cc-seat-dot cc-seat-dot--{{gradeClass}} {{statusClass}} {{#selected}}cc-seat-dot--selected{{/selected}}"
                                            data-seat-id="{{id}}"
                                            data-zone="{{../name}}"
                                            data-seat-name="{{seatNumber}}"
                                            data-seat-no="{{seatNo}}"
                                            data-grade="{{grade}}"
                                            data-price="{{priceText}}"
                                            aria-label="{{seatNumber}} {{grade}} {{priceText}}">
                                        <span class="cc-seat-no">{{seatNo}}</span>
                                        {{#selected}}<span class="cc-seat-check">✓</span>{{/selected}}
                                    </button>{{/seats}}
                            </div>
                        </section>
